race.comment: FIGURE IT OUT (3) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 4 length third over 425m at Bendigo, clocking 24.32. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. One of the leading chances. THAI TIGER (2) missed the frame latest when seventh at this track (25.81) but scored three back at this track (25.66). Got the money at his only try from this box. Should be in this for a long way. PAW JULIA (8) is likely to have admirers. Something for the Multiples: MILITANT STORM (4)
